<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <title>Batybot OAuth Setup - {{.UserType}} Authorization</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background: #0f0f23;
            color: #cccccc;
        }

        .container {
            background: #1a1a2e;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border: 1px solid #333;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #9146ff;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .auth-btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #9146ff;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px auto;
            display: block;
            width: 200px;
        }

        .auth-btn:hover {
            background: #772ce8;
        }

        .info {
            background: #2a2a3e;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #9146ff;
        }

        .warning {
            background: #3e2a2a;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #ff6b6b;
        }

        code {
            background: #2a2a3e;
            padding: 2px 6px;
            border-radius: 3px;
            font-family: monospace;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>ü¶á Batybot OAuth Setup - {{.UserType}} Authorization</h1>

        <div class="warning">
            <h3>‚ö†Ô∏è Important: Login as {{.ExpectedUser}}</h3>
            <p><strong>You must log in as the {{.UserType}} user: <code>{{.ExpectedUser}}</code></strong></p>
            <p>Make sure you're logged into Twitch as <strong>{{.ExpectedUser}}</strong> before clicking the
                authorization button.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="info">
            <h3>{{.UserType}} Authorization Required</h3>
            {{if eq .UserType "bot"}}
            <p>This step authorizes the bot user (<code>{{.ExpectedUser}}</code>) to:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Read and send chat messages</li>
                <li>Read and send whispers</li>
                <li>Basic bot functionality</li>
            </ul>
            {{else if eq .UserType "broadcaster"}}
            <p>This step authorizes the broadcaster (<code>{{.ExpectedUser}}</code>) to allow EventSub subscriptions
                for:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Subscription events (new subs, gift subs, resubs)</li>
                <li>Follow events</li>
                <li>Bits/Cheer events</li>
                <li>Chat notifications</li>
            </ul>
            {{end}}
        </div>

        <a href="{{.AuthURL}}" class="auth-btn">üîó Authorize {{.UserType}}</a>

        <div class="info">
            <p><strong>What happens next?</strong></p>
            <ol>
                <li>Click the authorize button above</li>
                <li><strong>Make sure you're logged in as {{.ExpectedUser}}</strong></li>
                <li>Authorize the application permissions</li>
                <li>You'll be redirected back here with your tokens</li>
                <li>{{if eq .UserType "bot"}}The bot will be ready for chat functionality{{else}}EventSub subscriptions
                    will be enabled{{end}}</li>
            </ol>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
